c: 30
v: 40
t: "Imana niyo yabaremye nukubaha imigisha yayo, hanyuma niyo izobica hanyuma ibazure, mbega muri bamwe mugereranya n’Imana yuko harimwo uwushobora kugira icarico cose muri ibi, rero itandukanye nuku gabanukirwa kukintu icarico cose kandi niyo iri hejuru gusumba kuvyo bayi gereranirizako"